<div class="callout home">

  <h1>Find your<br>natural<br>habitat.</h1>

</div>

<div class="row grey-row home comp-description">

  <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3">

    <h2>Choosing a job is difficult.  Because you don't just care about the zeroes on your paycheck.  You care about the million little daily interactions that are so much harder to capture.</h2>
    <h3>That's where Habitable excels.  We aggregate unskewed data from real employees about the companies you are interested in.  Then, using any information you choose to provide, we give you quantitative matches to companies that will feel like your natural habitat.</h3>

  </div>

</div>

<div class="row home submit-home">

    <%= form_tag new_user_registration_path, method: :get do %>

      <div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-2">
        <div class="form-group">
          <%= text_field_tag :industry, '', class: 'form-control', placeholder: 'Industry' %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="form-group">
          <%= text_field_tag :zip, '', class: 'form-control', placeholder: 'Zip Code' %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-2 col-md-offset-5">
        <%= submit_tag 'Sign Up', class: 'btn btn-default center-block submit'  %>
      </div>

    <% end %>

</div>